front.title: •Colonel Jendon in Onyx 1
front.gametext: May deploy as a 'react.'  Permanent pilot is •Jendon, who provides ability of 2.  When deployed, may deploy a weapon on Onyx 1 from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  Adds one battle destiny if with Onyx 2.  Immune to attrition < 4.
front.lore: Designed to emulate Rebel starfighter advantages. Production began shortly before the Battle of Endor. Armed with laser cannons, ion cannons and missile launchers.
